        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-03-23T20:24:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Playing it fast and loose with the terms “our pid” and “our own process.” Here, you mean |parent|. But to read this comment, it sounds more like you’re talking about this process, the test process that’s running this code right now.\n\nThis is one reason I like to avoid first-person plural in comments.",
      "revId": "3c1accd21450eb4a0248d2f0ed5e5a36e5e205dc",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
